Package com.zebra.sdk.common.card.containers

Provides containers for Zebra Card Printer objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlarmHandler
    This interface is used to signal when an alarm condition has occurred.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlarmInfo
    Container holding information about a printer alarm or error condition.
    BarcodeReadInfo
    Class for holding information read from the barcode.
    CardCountInfo
    Container holding the printers card count information.
    CardTypeInfo
    Class for getting and/or setting card type information.
    ZMotif Series re-transfer printers only.
    contained in DeviceUtilZmotif
    DiscoveryConfiguration
    Container holding the network discovery configuration parameters.
    GraphicsInfo
    Class for specifying the graphics information used during printing.
    JobConfigInfo
    Class for configuring a print jobs settings.
    JobSideConfigInfo
    Class for configuring the card side properties.
    JobStatus
    Class for holding the printer's job history information.
    JobStatusInfo
    Class for holding job status information for the specified job ID.
    LaminatorAdjustments
    Class for holding information about the Laminator's adjustment parameters.
    Part of container CardTypeInfo
    LaminatorCardCountInfo
    Container holding the Laminator's card count information.
    LaminatorInfo
    Class for holding information about the printer's Laminator.
    contained in ZebraPrinterZmotif
    MagConfigInfo
    Class for configuring a magnetic encoding job.
    MagneticEncoderInfo
    Class for getting the printer's magnetic encoder configuration.
    MagneticEncoderOffsetInfo
    Class for getting and/or setting the magnetic encoder offset values.
    MagSentinel
    Class for getting and/or setting the individual magnetic encoder track sentinel configurations.
    ZMotif Series printers only.
    MagTrackData
    Class for magnetic encoder track data.
    MediaInfo
    Class for holding information about the printer's installed media.
    MemoryInfo
    Class for getting the printer's available memory.
    ZMotif Series printers only.
    NetworkInfo
    Class for getting and/or setting the printer's wired network configuration.
    OCPDisplayInfo
    Class for getting and/or setting the printer's OCP line data.
    OCPLine
    Class for getting and/or setting the printer's OCP line data.
    OCPSettings
    Container for getting and/or setting the printer's OCP configuration.
    ParameterInfo
    Class for holding information about a settings value and range.
    PrinterInfo
    Class for holding information about a printer.
    PrinterStatusInfo
    Class for getting the printer's current status information.
    ReservationInfo
    Class for getting the printer's reservation information.
    ZMotif printers only.
    SmartCardInfo
    Class for holding the printers smart card configuration information.
    TemplateJob
    Class for holding data to be rendered during card template printing
    TransferSpeeds
    Class for holding information for card type specific transfer speed offsets for the ZXP8 Series printers.
    Part of container CardTypeInfo
    TransferTemps
    Class for holding information for card type specific transfer temperature offsets for the ZXP8 Series printers.
    Part of container CardTypeInfo
    WirelessAccessPointInfo
    Class for holding information about the discovered wireless access points.
    WirelessNetworkInfo
    Class for holding information about the printer's wireless network configuration.
    ZMotif Series printers only.
